\id TIT YAWU - Foreman 15/7/95
\h TAITUS
\toc1 Pol ere Taitus erne bas rasem siglou
\toc2 Taitus
\toc3 Taitus
\mt1 TAITUS
\mt2 Pol ere Taitus erne bas rasem siglou.
\is1 Kiyi late tuma.
\ip Gwote siglou Pol ere bas rasen Taitus erne newopitim. Taitus ere Juda tame berai, ere akeite kantriri tame. Ere God eri tuma worwor meten ere Kristen tem. Kristen tem, ere Pol eterken yaku kere tamesip tem. Sene ere Krit ailanke yim, ere Kristen lakerete yaku etek kerebetem.
\is1 Pol ere Taitus erne bas rasem tuma gwo.
\ip Sapta 1—3. Krit ailanke tetan Kristen tatame etemne Taitus ere muresen etemri kenawaike abobe wule eyarte, etemri tetankap eyarte.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 An Pol, an God eteri yaku kerebe tame. An Krais Jisas eteri aposel yaku kerebe tame. God ere kiyi wom taken tameken emne ere ane won yim, an ete taken tameken emne kobo labe, eme God erne kenawaike abobe, eme tuma seken noub metbe. Etepkap eme God eri wule noub sebe.
\v 2 Ete tuma seken eme kenawaike mette, eme noub som temente. Eke eme etep abon kouten. Kiyisapewai God ere nowsel mak seikmenem, ere etep wom. Ane kenawaike abote tatame eme noub som temente nenbe. Etep wom, Apei God ere tuma yikwokwobe tame berai. Eri wom tuma e seken tem.
\v 3 Etep wom, yuri God eteri wom yabelke ere tame emne won eme eri tuma wusowum, eteri tuma ere genik tem. Nemne Sene Petbe God eter ere ane won yim, an ete tuma wusoube.
\p 
\v 4 Taitus, an gwote siglou nene bas rasbe. Nerem God erne kenawaike abobekap, ne etep kir som abobe, ne ari yen seken.
\p Apei God eter, neremne Sene Petbe Tame Krais Jisas eter, epe nene pap yewon noub nente, ne pap yenbo temente.
\s1 Taitus ere tame yenbo emne yaku newote, eme Kristen tatame etemri lakerebe tame tete.
\p 
\v 5 An nene mesginim, an nene Krit ailan eteke mesginim. Mesginte nenem, an nene etep wom. Kau yaku nema beke kere, ete yaku ne keren omote. Ne kom komke yin Kristen lakere tame emne kenete. Etep wom. An nene womkap, ne etepke tete.
\v 6 Etepkap tame emne ne kenete. Taken tameken eme ete tame erne yenbowou wobe. Ere ta wurisubu paneten. Eri yen eme Aneyen Jisas erne kenawaike abobe. Eri yen emne tatame eme ete yen emne etep beke kip wo. Eme wule yaper nenbe, eme anenawo epri tuma naswoibe. Tatame eme etep beke kip wo. Eike tame eme etepkap yen temente, etepkap tame ne emne mane kenete.
\v 7 Eike tame eme God eteri yaku kerete, eme God eteri tatame emne lakerebe yaku kerete, eke eme wule yenbowou nenbetete. Ete tame emne akeite tatame eme emri wule yaper beke wuri la. Eme tawul pes beke kip te. Eme pap agetage beke kip waye. Eme ok yaper an sisi beke kip pe. Eme tatame etemken ei beke kip nai. Eme kel petbe pap beke kip te.
\v 8 Ete wos eme beke kip nen. Eme gwopke nenbe. Eme sipkom yabe tatame emne a newon abe, emne tukna emi newobe. Eme wule yenbo metekwasbe. Eme selpap yenbowou nenbe. Eme tame yenbo. Eme God eteri wule noub tobobe. Eme mureken, eke eme wule yaper nente pap beke kip waye, eme ete wule magel taibe, eme beke kip nen.
\v 9 Eme kiyi kenawaike metem tuma seken eme kenawaike som abon tobote. Etep tobote, eme ete tuma seken eri somo tatame emne wusoute, eme noub me temente. Eme tuma noub wusoute, tuma seken naswoibe tatame eme emri nenbe wule yaperkap noub abote.
\s1 Tuma yikwokobe tame nogwape eme Kritke temenem.
\p 
\v 10 Tame nogwape eme tuma seken beke tobo. Eme tumak bepou me wobe, eme yikwokwo yakwokwobe tuma wobe. Somo kwunbe tame nogwape etem eme etep nenbe.
\v 11 Ete tame eme tatame emne bepou me yikwokwo tuma wusoube, eme emri kel petbe. Yaper nente wule eme etep wusoube. Tame nogwape emri yentaken eme emri tuma metbe, eme emri elemoi lubutbe. Ete yikwokwo yakwokwo tuma wobe tame emne ne wotakete.
\v 12 Kiyiri Krit tame wuri ere porereken tame, ere etep wom. Krit komri tatame eme akei, eme tuma yikwokwobe tatame. Eme por wale tebekap, eme awos nogwape kenake abe. Eme yaku bul worabe. Etep wom.
\v 13 Eri wom tuma e tuma seken. Eke ne emne noub wote, eme emri nenbe wule yaper mesginin eme God erne kenawaike sene abote.
\v 14 Eme Juda emri akeite akeite sukuyeta bepou sene beke kip met. God eteri tuma seken magel taibe tame emri tuma eme sene beke kip meten nen.
\v 15 Selpap yenbo tetan tatame eme labe, akei wos e yenbo. Selpap yaper tetan kenawaike beke abo tatame eme labe, akei wos e yaper. Emri selpap, emri porere e yaper, eke eme etep labe.
\v 16 Etemri elemoike eme etep wobe. An God erne abobe. Emri nenbekap nema etep labe, e kena, e yaper. Etep tebe, eme God erne magel taibe. God ere emri nenbekap mowai wobe. Eme God eri tuma naswoyin wan gwolebe. Etepkap, eme wule yenbo mapeke nen?
\c 2
\s1 Ta keryen tame keryen eme God eteri wule yenbo sete.
\p 
\v 1 Neren, ne tatame emne tuma yenbo somoken noub wusoute.
\v 2 Ne emne etep wote. Tame keryen eme ok yaper mane an sisi pete. Eme wule yenbowou abote. Eme emri selpap wusom noub lakerete, eme wule yaper mane nente. Eme kenawaike abobe wule yenbo som sete. Eme kobo labe wule som sete. Be wos yaper emne tete, eme God erne beke kip mesgin.
\p 
\v 3 Ta keryen eme gwopkap wule nente. Tatame eme God erne kenawaike abon yenbo nenbekap, eme etepwou nente. Eme kerebe tuma mane wote. Eme ok yaper abe wule eteri kulke mane wurte. Eme wule yenbo peterate.
\v 4 Eme mungu ta emne wule yenbo wusoute, mungu ta eme gwopkap wule nente. Eme emri yenken tameken emne noub abon yenbo nente.
\v 5 Eme emri selpap noub lakerete, eme yaper mane nente. Eme sir mane yite. Eme emri yenken tameken emne noub nente. Eme tame etemri tuma meten yenbo nente. Etep nente, epkap tatame eme God eri wule mapeke yaper wo? Berai.
\s1 Taitus ere wule yenbo nente, tame taureyen eme lan kir nente.
\p 
\v 6 Tame taureyen emne ne kir wote. Eme gwopkap wule nente. Eme emri wusomken selpapken noub lakeren wos yaper mane nente.
\v 7 Neren kir, be wos be wos ne nente, ne wule yenbowou nente. Etep nente, ne tame taureyen emne wule yenbo peterate. Tuma wusoube yaku ne som kerete, ne tuma sekenwou wote. Sou tuma yaper mane wote.
\v 8 Ne tuma yenbowou wote, neri peiktame eme nene tuma mapeke wote? Eme nene tuma wolawoyin, eme sebera yate nenbe.
\s1 Yaku kerebe tame eme yaku lakerebe tame etemri tuma mette.
\p 
\v 9 Ne kel yaku kerebe tame emne wote, eme gwopkap wule nente. Eme yaku lakerebe tame etemri kulke temente. Etepkap, lakerebe tame eme emri yaku metekwaste, eke eme yaku yenbowou kerete, eme emri tuma mane naswoite.
\v 10 Eme emri wos sirke mane pette. Eme wos yaper mane nente. Kwokwos kwokwos eme emri yaku yenbowou kerebet. Etep tete, neremne Sene Petbe Tame God eteri tuma ere sig yenbo pette.
\s1 Nema God eteri wule yenbo nenen yin Krais eter yate nenbe yabel noub kowun simente.
\p 
\v 11 God ere akei tatame emne kobo lan sene pette wule genik tem.
\v 12 Ete wule ere nemne etep wobe. Nema God erne magel sene mane taite, nema nowselri wos mesginte. Nema porere yenbo nente, nema yenbowou nente. Nema God eteri wule noub sete. Nema temente, nema etepwou nente.
\v 13 Nema etep tetan, nema wos yenbosubu metekwasen kouten. Neremri Keryen God eisau, nemne Sene Petbe Tame, Jisas Krais, epri yenbo tetankap, ere kom genik tete nenbe. Nema eteke koute.
\v 14 Kiyi nema yaperwai temenem, Jisas Krais ere nemne kobo lan sam. Ere nerem nenbetem wule yaper peten sepitim, nemne sene petem. Sene petem, nema eteri tatame yenbo tem, nema wule yenbowou nente pap etewouke tebe.
\p 
\v 15 Ete tuma ne tatame emne wusoute. Ne emne ete tuma wote, eme ete tuma noub meten tobote. Wule yaper nenbe tatame emne ne emne noub wote, eme wule yaper mesginte. God ere nene ete yaku newom, eke tatame eme nene yaper mane wote, nene mane teitkwunte.
\c 3
\s1 God ere nemne noub nenem, eke nema wule yenbo nente.
\p 
\v 1 Ne tatame emri selpap etepke tagwote. Eme kaunsil tameken gavman tameken etemri kulke temente, emri tuma noub mette. Be yaku yenbo gavman eme emne wote, eme agetage noub kerete.
\v 2 Eme tatame emne tuma yaper mane won mane naswoite. Eme ei mane nakwosete. Eme etemken tuma yenbo elen me namdete. Eme akei taken tameken emne wule yenbowou peterabetete.
\p 
\v 3 Kiyi nerem, nema me eikse aksebetem. Nema tuma naswoibetem. Nema gabo etem yikwokwobetem tuma meten epkap epkap wule yaper ere nemne keresukbetem. Wule yaper nema nente pap wayebetem, nema metekwasen etepwou nenbetem. Kwokwos kwokwos nema tatama emne pap yaper ten wurkwoyeken resbetem. Nema tatame emri wos pap etewouke tebetem. Tatame eme nemne mo won kobo beke la. Nema emne awoawo mo won kobo labetem.
\v 4 Sene neremne Sene Petbe Tame God eteri kobo lan noub nenbe wule ere genik tem.
\v 5 Nema erne kenawaike abobetem, eke ere nemne sene petem. Nema wos yenbo wuri beke nen, eke ere nemne bepou sene petem. Eter, ere nemne kobo lan nemne baptais ok wiruwum, nema tatama ager sene ek tem, God Eri Wou ere nemne eyarem.
\v 6 Neremne Sene Petbe Tame, Jisas Krais eterke God ere Eri Wou nemne noub newom.
\v 7 Etek kobo labe wulek God ere nemne tatame yenbo wobe. Ere nemne tuma sene beke kip wo, nemne yaper awosein beke kip nen. Berai. Etep ten, ere womkap, nema noub som temente. Nema etepkap temente, eke nema kenawaike abon kouten.
\p 
\v 8 E tuma seken. An nene wusoube tuma ne emne noub wusoubetete, an etep abobe. Etep tete, God erne kenawaike abobe tatame eme noub abon wos yenbo nogwape muresen nenbet. Eme etep tete, e yenbo. E tatame emne kobo labe.
\v 9 Metye. Eikseten tuma, yeiwarege etemri sig, ne ei tuma etemken mane som walekap naite. God ere Moses erne newom wule tuma ne etemken walekap mane naite. Etep tete, etepkap e tatame emne kobo beke kip la. Berai.
\p 
\v 10 Tame ere Kristen etemken walekap nayin eme kenakena tete wote, ne erne tewo pes wotakete. Etep tete, ere neri tuma beke kip met, kem erne magel taite.
\v 11 Etepkap tame, ere selpap yaper som tetan. E seken. Eter ere maime kena yaper wobe.
\s1 Taitus ere Pol erne yin late.
\p 
\v 12 Yuri an Artemas eterne o Tikikus eterne won nene yan late, ne kelu lan Nikopolis komke ane agetage yan late. Woru tete, an ete komke temente.
\v 13 Wule metbe, porereken tame Senasken Apolosken epe ete komke yite wote, ne epne kobo late. Epe be wos be wos mane eiksete.
\v 14 Neremri Kristen tatame eme wule wuri pette. Eme wule yenbo muresen nenbet. Eme bepou mane temente, eke eme wos eiksebe tatame emne kobo late.
\p 
\v 15 Arenken tetan tatame eme akei eme nene pir wobe. God erne kenawaike abobe tamenowu emne ne wote, nema emne pir wobe.
\m God ere kemne pap yewon noub nente.
\p Pol ere bas rasem tuma ab eteke. 
